---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---


<Layout title="Undercarriage & GET - PT Pilarindo Jaya Abadi" >

    <div class="bg-white mt-20">

        <main class="mx-auto px-4 pb-24 pt-14 sm:px-6 sm:pb-32 sm:pt-16 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
            <!-- Product -->
            <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-7 lg:grid-rows-1 lg:gap-x-8 lg:gap-y-10 xl:gap-x-16">
                <!-- Product image -->
                <div class="lg:col-span-4 lg:row-end-1">
                    <div class="aspect-h-3 aspect-w-4 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-gray-100">
                        <!-- Gambar Excavator Track / Undercarriage -->
                        <img src="product-2.jpg"
                             alt="Heavy Equipment Undercarriage Parts"
                             class="object-cover object-center bg-repeat">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Product details -->
                <div class="mx-auto mt-14 max-w-2xl sm:mt-16 lg:col-span-3 lg:row-span-2 lg:row-end-2 lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none">
                    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse">
                        <div class="mt-4">
                            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-3xl">
                                Undercarriage & Ground Engaging Tools (GET)
                            </h1>

                            <h2 id="information-heading" class="sr-only">Informasi Produk</h2>
                            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
                                Kategori: Mining & Construction (Komatsu / CAT / Hitachi / Kobelco)
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <p class="mt-6 text-gray-500">
                        Solusi total untuk kaki-kaki alat berat Anda. Kami menyediakan rangkaian lengkap <i>Track Link</i>, <i>Track Shoe</i>, <i>Roller</i>, <i>Idler</i>, dan <i>Sprocket</i> yang dirancang khusus untuk medan tambang ekstrem di Indonesia. Dilengkapi dengan <i>Bucket Teeth</i> (Kuku Bucket) berbahan baja keras untuk penetrasi tanah yang maksimal.
                    </p>

                    <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-6 gap-y-4 sm:grid-cols-1">
                        <button type="button"
                                class="flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-black bg-black px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-black focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2">
                            Minta Penawaran Harga
                        </button>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-10 border-t border-gray-200 pt-10">
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Keunggulan Utama</h3>
                        <div class="prose prose-sm mt-4 text-gray-500">

                            <ul role="list" class="space-y-6">
                                <li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
                                    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex w-6 justify-center -bottom-6">
                                        <div class="w-px bg-gray-200"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white">
                                        <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-600 ring-1 ring-gray-300"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500"><span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Heavy Duty Heat Treatment</span> Melalui proses pengerasan khusus untuk ketahanan aus maksimal.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
                                    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex w-6 justify-center -bottom-6">
                                        <div class="w-px bg-gray-200"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white">
                                        <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-600 ring-1 ring-gray-300"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500"><span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Deep Hardened Surface</span> Kedalaman kekerasan optimal mencegah keretakan dini.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
                                    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex w-6 justify-center -bottom-6">
                                        <div class="w-px bg-gray-200"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white">
                                        <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-600 ring-1 ring-gray-300"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500"><span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Wide Compatibility</span> Tersedia untuk unit 20 ton hingga 200 ton (PC200 - PC2000 / D85 - D375).</p>
                                </li>
                                <li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
                                    <div class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white">
                                        <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-600 ring-1 ring-gray-300"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500"><span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Cost Effective</span> Kualitas setara OEM dengan harga yang jauh lebih kompetitif.</p>
                                </li>
                            </ul>

                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-10 border-t border-gray-200 pt-10">
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Spesifikasi Teknis</h3>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
                            Material Forged Steel & Boron Steel. Hardness level mencapai HRC 52-56 untuk area kontak kritis. Seal groups menggunakan desain duo-cone floating seal untuk mencegah kebocoran oli pelumas.
                        </p>
                    </div>


                </div>

                <div class="mx-auto mt-16 w-full max-w-2xl lg:col-span-4 lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none">
                    <div>
                        <div class="border-b border-gray-200">
                            <div class="-mb-px flex space-x-8" aria-orientation="horizontal" role="tablist">
                                <button id="tab-faq"
                                        class="border-transparent text-gray-700 hover:border-gray-300 hover:text-gray-800 whitespace-nowrap border-b-2 py-6 text-sm font-medium"
                                        aria-controls="tab-panel-faq" role="tab" type="button">FAQ Produk
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div id="tab-panel-faq" class="text-sm text-gray-500" aria-labelledby="tab-faq" role="tabpanel"
                             tabindex="0">
                            <h3 class="sr-only">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>

                            <dl>
                                <dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">Apakah ada garansi jam operasi (Hours Warranty)?</dt>
                                <dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
                                    <p>
                                        Ya, untuk pembelian satu set lengkap (Full Set Undercarriage), kami memberikan garansi pemakaian hingga 2.000 - 4.000 jam operasional (tergantung kondisi medan dan tipe unit), yang mencakup cacat produksi atau keausan prematur.
                                    </p>
                                </dd>
                                <dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">Apakah melayani pemasangan di site (On-site Installation)?</dt>
                                <dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
                                    <p>
                                        Tentu. Kami memiliki tim mekanik yang siap dikirim ke lokasi tambang (Kalimantan, Sumatera, Sulawesi) untuk melakukan penggantian undercarriage (R&I) dengan biaya tambahan yang terjangkau.
                                    </p>
                                </dd>
                                <dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">Stok apa yang paling cepat tersedia?</dt>
                                <dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
                                    <p>
                                        Kami menjaga stok <i>fast moving</i> untuk unit populer seperti Komatsu PC200, PC300, D85, dan Caterpillar 320, D6, D8. Untuk unit <i>giant</i> seperti PC1250 atau PC2000, mohon konfirmasi ketersediaan stok terlebih dahulu.
                                    </p>
                                </dd>

                            </dl>
                        </div>


                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </main>


    </div>


</Layout>
